02/07/2004
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- Defence Minister Nikolai Svinarov and his Macedonian counterpart, Vlado Buckovski, met on Friday (2 July) in Sofia. Their meeting focused on ways Bulgaria might help Macedonia guard its airspace sovereignty. The meeting took place in the framework of an international conference on NATO membership, under way in Sofia. (BNT; Dnevnik - 02/07/04)
